Magpie
```json
{
"application": "Magpie",
"software": [
{
"name": "Hadoop",
"version": "3.3.1",
"setup": true,
"setup_type": "MR",
"home": "${HOME}/hadoop-${HADOOP_VERSION}",
"local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/hadoop",
"conf_files": "${HOME}/myconf",
"daemon_heap_max": 2000,
"namenode_heap_max": 2000,
"environment_extra": "${HOME}/hadoop-my-environment",
"job": "terasort",
"max_tasks_per_node": 8,
"default_map_tasks": 8,
"default_reduce_tasks": 8,
"child_heapsize": 2048,
"child_map_heapsize": 2048,
"child_reduce_heapsize": 4096,
"child_map_container_buffer": 256,
"child_reduce_container_buffer": 512,
"mapreduce_slowstart": 0.05,
"container_memory": 32768,
"check_memory_limits": true,
"compression": false,
"io_sort_factor": 10,
"io_sort_mb": 100,
"parallel_copies": 10,
"terasort_size": 50000000,
"teragen_map_count": 4,
"terasort_reducer_count": 4,
"terasort_clear_cache": true,
"terasort_output_replication": 1,
"terasort_run_terachecksum": false,
"terasort_run_teravalidate": false,
"decommission_hdfs_node_size": 8,
"filesystem_mode": "hdfsoverlustre",
"local_filesystem_blocksize": 33554432,
"hdfs_replication": 3,
"hdfs_blocksize": 134217728,
"hdfs_path": "/ssd/${USER}/hdfs",
"hdfs_path_clear": "yes",
"hdfsoverlustre_path": "/lustre/${USER}/hdfsoverlustre/",
"hdfsoverlustre_remove_locks": true,
"hdfsovernetworkfs_path": "/networkfs/${USER}/hdfsovernetworkfs/",
"hdfsovernetworkfs_remove_locks": true,
"rawnetworkfs_path": "/lustre/${USER}/rawnetworkfs/",
"localstore": "/ssd/${USER}/localstore/",
"localstore_clear": "yes"
},
{
"name": "Hive",
"version": "2.3.0",
"setup": true,
"port": 10000,
"home": "${HOME}/apache-hive-${HIVE_VERSION}-bin",
"local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/hive",
"metastore_dir": "/lustre/${USER}/hive/database/postgres/data",
"use_tez": false,
"tez_version": "0.9.1",
"tez_home": "${HOME}/apache-tez-${TEZ_VERSION}-bin",
"job": "testbench",
"testbench_dir": "${HOME}/hive-testbench",
"testbench_type": "tpch",
"cli_version": "beeline",
"testbench_data_size": 2,
"testbench_query_count": 4
},
{
"name": "Zookeeper",
"version": "3.4.14",
"setup": true,
"replication_count": 3,
"share_nodes": false,
"job": "zookeeperruok",
"home": "${HOME}/zookeeper-${ZOOKEEPER_VERSION}",
"conf_files": "${HOME}/myconf",
"data_dir": "/lustre/${USER}/zookeeper",
"data_dir_clear": "yes",
"data_dir_type": "networkfs",
"local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/zookeeper",
"ticktime": 2000,
"initlimit": 20,
"synclimit": 10
},
{
"name": "PostgreSQL",
"home": "${HOME}/pgsql",
"port": 11115,
"data_dir": "/lustre/${USER}/hive/database/postgres/data",
"db_name": "hive_default_db"
}
],
"resource_requirements": {
"nodes": "<my_node_count>",
"time": "<my_time_in_hours:minutes>",
"queue": "<my_queue>",
"scripts_home": "${HOME}/magpie",
"local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/magpie",
"java_home": "/usr/lib/jvm/jre-1.8.0/",
"remote_cmd": "ssh",
"remote_cmd_opts": ""
},
"other": {
"submission_type": "lsfmpirun",
"job_type": "hive",
"job_script": "${HOME}/my-job-script",
"startup_time": 30,
"shutdown_time": 30,
"one_time_run": "yes",
"pre_job_run": "${MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME}/scripts/pre-job-run-scripts/my-pre-job-script",
"post_job_run": "${MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME}/scripts/post-job-run-scripts/my-post-job-script",
"pre_execute_run": "${MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME}/scripts/pre-job-run-scripts/my-pre-job-script",
"post_execute_run": "${MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME}/scripts/post-job-run-scripts/my-post-job-script",
"environment_variable_script": "${HOME}/my-job-env",
"environment_variable_script_shell": "/bin/bash",
"mpirun_options": "-genvall -genv MV2_USE_APM 0"
}
}
```
